data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom custom home with a wonderful yard, double-bay garage, and RV parking nestled on a tranquil dead-end street in the charming town of Myrtle Point, Oregon. With thoughtful design and attention to detail, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and natural beauty; a light-filled and open-concept living space. The main level features both a living room and sitting/family room, perfect for gathering with loved ones or relaxing after a long day.   There is also a bedroom/office on the first floor as well as a half bath. The kitchen is a true chef's delight, equipped with granite countertops, cook island, and ample cabinetry. Whether you're preparing a family meal or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is sure to be the heart of the home. The owner's suite is located upstairs along with 2 ample sized bedrooms and the oversized bonus room with reading nooks in each dormer and 2 back decks.
